<br>
Wrong!  At high levels lots of zones are indoors.  It is definitely not convenient and you're certainly not going to hold up your experience group or raiding party while you go to an outdoor zone to refresh SoW.  You're right, you probably won't often use increased run speed to escape monsters, but you will need it to keep up with the rest of your party.<br>
<br>
Jboots?  Horse?  If you've died and are on your way back to your corpse you won't have those those with you.<br>
<br>
Unless you solo a lot (which I understand is the case on Firiona Vie), you probably don't especially need additional run speed immediately after obtaining level 51 (although you'll probably want it before 60) unless you pull a lot in indoor zones, e.g., ToV.  <br>
<br>
As far as the rest of the AA abilities, they can definitely wait until after you reach 60. <p><b>Trésjoli Louveteau<b>
